<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>* <span class="c2">(فَرْعٌ)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فِي مَذَاهِبِ الْعُلَمَاءِ فِي اجْتِمَاعِ الْعُشْرِ وَالْخَرَاجِ مَذْهَبُنَا اجْتِمَاعُهُمَا وَلَا يَمْنَعُ أَحَدُهُمَا وُجُوبَ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>